      <h2>QuestionnaireItemUsageMode</h2>
      <div>
        <p>Identifies the modes of usage of a questionnaire that should enable a particular questionnaire item</p>

      </div>
      <p>This code system http://hl7.org/fhir/questionnaire-usage-mode defines the following codes:</p>
      <table class="codes">
        <tr>
          <td>
            <b>Code</b>
          </td>
          <td>
            <b>Display</b>
          </td>
